  <bioghist id="aspace_f299269df18375191c8ee0fd9f9fc3bb">
    <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
<p>Morris Paris was a radio news commentator for WEVD, and assistant deputy controller of New York, N.Y. from 1938 to 1963.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_c78676527af60cb21560ddc0732e2be1">
    <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
<p>The papers contain typewritten manuscripts of "Review of the Week" (1943-1946), news commentary on WEVD, the Jewish Daily Forward Radio Station. Papers also include a series of articles titled, "Limited Dividend Housing becomes a Racket" (1934).</p>  </scopecontent>
